list.title: Best of Paris in 7 day Tour
list.info: Paris often referred to as the  is renowned for its rich history, culture, and iconic landmarks. There are numerous tours available in Paris that cater to various interests and preferences. Here's an overview of some popular types of tours you can find in Paris Walking Tours These tours typically focus on exploring specific neighborhoods or attractions on foot. You can find guided walking tours of landmarks like the Eiffel Tower Notre-Dame Cathedral Montmartry the Latin Quarter and more. Walking tours offer a more intimate experience and allow you to soak in the atmosphere of the city
